text: The Philippine Daily Inquirer, commonly known as the Inquirer, is a broadsheet newspaper in the Philippines. Its headquarters is in Makati City. It was founded in December 9, 1985. ==References== ==Other websites== * Official website Category:National newspapers published in the Philippines Category:English-language newspapers published in Asia Category:1985 establishments in Asia Category:1980s establishments in the Philippines
